<span id="an_8:22">8:22</span> Jischpan, Eber, Eliel,

<span id="an_8:23">8:23</span> Abdon, Zicri, Hanan,

<span id="an_8:24">8:24</span> Hanania, Elam, Anthothija,

<span id="an_8:25">8:25</span> Jiphdeja et Penuel étaient fils de
